  <summary date="2022-11-09T19:29:44Z" status="Introduced in House">Providing for Unhoused People with Pets Act of 2022 or the PUPP Act of 2022

This bill permits the Department of Housing and Urban Development to award grants for interim and permanent housing that accommodates individuals (or families) who are homeless and have pets. Entities eligible for the grant include local governments, nonprofits, and entities that house or shelter homeless individuals.</summary>
